    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "You seem to be using `  const content = hit._highlightResult.html.value;` in your code (`hitTemplate`); but some hits don't have `html`, which causes the error to show up. You should try/catch that and instead give a default value of `\"\"`. Can you try that? ",
